      },
      "widgets_values": [
        "## GPU:RTX4090D 24GB\n\n| Configuration            | VRAM Usage | 1st Generation | 2nd Generation |\n|---------------------|---------------|---------------|-----------------|\n| Fp8_e4m3fn             | 86%                | ≈ 94s               | ≈ 71s                   |\n| With 8steps LoRA    | 86%                | ≈ 55s               | ≈ 34s                  |\n| Distill fp8_e4m3fn   | 86%                | ≈ 69s               | ≈ 36s                  |"
      ],
      "color": "#222",
      "bgcolor": "#000"
    },
